critter.name: Rajah Brooke's Birdwing
critter.desc: ...I must say, I'm quite impressed with your ability to catch such an impressive butterfly... The Raja Brooke butterfly, I must tell you, is one of the larger tiger butterflies. Naturally, its antennae and proboscis also rank as some of the largest around. Be not proud, vile beast! Your cute red collar and fancy name do not fool Blathers!
critter.quote: I caught a Rajah Brooke birdwing! Nothing else I'd rajah be doing!
